{"tid":1183024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"守護香港反送中  日期：2019年6月9日 時間：2:30集合；3:00起步 地點：銅鑼灣東角道 至 立法會","createTime":"2019-06-02T15:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T16:53:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cffc1811e9fc26fcdb62c83015170b26a3ea4a6c","tid":1183024,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:23:39.000Z","msg":"民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front <br />\n<br />\n守護香港反送中<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年6月9日<br />\n時間：2:30集合；3:00起步<br />\n地點：銅鑼灣東角道 至 立法會<br />\n<br />\nNo extradition to China, march for our Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nDate: June 9, 2019 (Sun) Time: rally@14:30; march@3:00<br />\nVenue: East Point Road, Causeway Bay -&gt; LegCo<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/60603206_2261822703865108_4329127911094222848_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=982464192ffade75e9f92d048225409d&amp;oe=5D94FC87\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F60603206_2261822703865108_4329127911094222848_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D982464192ffade75e9f92d048225409d%26oe%3D5D94FC87&h=ae76a059&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a717d11d84d0a9e4f27de8853dadb0d3be9b4083","tid":1183024,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:24:11.000Z","msg":"嚟緊既星期日"},{"pid":"59048d059a5a5638649ac9efbd86195f48cb471e","tid":1183024,"uid":84267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T15:29:09.000Z","msg":"唔係黑警唔批, 改左維園出發咩<br />\n<br />\n班垃圾黑警最叻係呢D時候搞小動作<br />\n混淆班人"},{"pid":"98b07c5163ce98e759d101907b738702da26b7c7","tid":1183024,"uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">最新資訊,  估計好多人,  維園草地起步</span></span><br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front<br />\n<br />\n6月9日反「送中」大遊行，最新安排如下：<br />\n<br />\n遊行起點：<span style=\"color: orange;\">銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）</span><br />\n遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n<br />\n參與遊行呼籲：<br />\n<br />\n1. 想與民陣一同起步的遊行參與者，在維園草地集合。<br />\n<br />\n*2. 坐輪椅人士、有需要人士或推嬰兒車的照顧者，可以維園草地旁的「南路」集合，民陣會安排優先出發。<br />\n<br />\n3. 想中途加入遊行的參與者，可在軒尼斯道西行線（往灣仔方向，於銅鑼灣波斯富街之後的路段加入。但必須在帶頭車及遊行帶頭橫額之後，才加入遊行隊伍。）<br />\n<br />\n4. 請所有參與遊行的市民，就長時間遊行做好充足的準備，包括：水、毛巾、手機充電、雨傘、電風扇等等。<br />\n<br />\n無懼政權打壓，6月9日，全港總動員，反「送中」、撤惡法！<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線秘書處<br />\n<br />\n#遊行已獲發不反對通知書<br />\n#警方大石壓死蟹<br />\n#警權無限大<br />\n#人權被出賣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/61620734_2281134285267283_2809325987915890688_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=16575c49eeeb52ed852610bdb4b9c290&amp;oe=5D50D13E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F61620734_2281134285267283_2809325987915890688_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3D16575c49eeeb52ed852610bdb4b9c290%26oe%3D5D50D13E&h=f983196d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.680202458693815/2281134281933950/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.680202458693815%2F2281134281933950%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=803f8feb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.680202458693815/2281134281933950/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"b53d3e3908222eb9161c60250a6bf30740582a25","tid":1183024,"uid":226955,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:20:36.000Z","msg":"改咗地點去維園呢樣嘢要加緊宣傳，因為之前東角道已經宣傳咗一段日子"},{"pid":"9c2dc20a5a709b195292277bd59a0f6147e1db87","tid":1183024,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:20:49.000Z","msg":"巴打成日遊行都有你份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc7420e80157ff19bbc853687d7b96deff7d615","tid":1183024,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">-簽完記得確認返電郵</span><br />\n好重要所以要講三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=871791ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（全球聯署、白宮聯署、學界、各行各業、宗教、地區/ 海外港人等等）反送中聯署合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY%2Fhtmlview&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=72785d8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QvnvG9YxQ5Vd5Ok-EejV1oAkLe_tDW_7qaWbjcZADMY/htmlview</a>"},{"pid":"9497a30526f3794d87de5bcb56e620c530c853ac","tid":1183024,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c2dc20a5a709b195292277bd59a0f6147e1db87"